Class UserComponent

  • java.lang.Object
    • UserComponent
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    User, UserGroup

    public abstract class UserComponent
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is a parent abstract class of User and UserGroup class. Each UserComponent has a tree node for itself. This class is useful for the composite pattern.
